						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/European-Institute-of-Innovation-and-Technology-EIT" title="European Institute of Innovation and Technology (EIT)" alt="link">European Institute of Innovation and Technology (EIT)</a></h2>

	
					<p>The European Institute of Innovation and Technology (EIT) brings together higher education institutions, research centres and businesses and aims to build Knowledge and Innovation Communities (KICs, a type of cross-border public-private-partnerships). To date, three KICs have been created, focusing on sustainable energy, climate change and information and communication society. The EIT should set up a KIC in 2014 on ‘Food for the future’ that will examine sustainable supply chains. <a href="http://eit.europa.eu/" target="_blank">Click to visit the EIT’s website</a>(<a href="http://eit.europa.eu/" target="_blank">EIT</a>, 7/11/2012)</p>
							<p><span class="date">8/02/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/European-Institute-of-Innovation-and-Technology-EIT">Read more...</a>
</div>
