						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="article" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Documents-Expert-Consultation-Agricultural-Innovation-Systems-CTA-COS-SiS-February-2013" title="Documents: Expert Consultation 'Agricultural Innovation Systems' CTA / COS-SiS February 2013 " alt="article">Documents: Expert Consultation 'Agricultural Innovation Systems' CTA / COS-SiS February 2013 </a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p>On this page, you will find all the documents (presentations and <b>draft</b> papers) produced for the&nbsp;<b>CTA/CoS-SIS Expert Consultation on Innovation Systems: 'Towards more effective theories of change'&nbsp;</b>04-06 February 2013, CTA Headquarters, the Netherlands.&nbsp;The <b>programme</b> and <b>concept note</b> of the event can be downloaded <a href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-events/Expert-consultation-on-innovation-systems-Towards-more-effective-theories-of-change" target="_blank">here</a>.Scroll down to find the presentation(s) or paper(s) you are looking for.</p>
